org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.query

Interface BaseQueryBuilder<T,Q extends BaseQuery<T,?>,R extends BaseQueryBuilder<T,Q,R>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the entries
    Q - the type of query (AggregationQuery or Query)
    R - the type of the builder, useful for extensions of this to maintain type
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AggregationQueryBuilder<P,R,T,A>, QueryBuilder<T,R>, VectorAggregationQueryBuilder<P,R>, VectorQueryBuilder
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AggregationQueryBuilderImpl, BaseQueryBuilderImpl, QueryBuilderImpl, VectorAggregationQueryBuilderImpl, VectorQueryBuilderImpl

    public interface BaseQueryBuilder<T,Q extends BaseQuery<T,?>,R extends BaseQueryBuilder<T,Q,R>>
    A base class for building queries
